-- Mega Event Structures
('German Aluminum Hangars (20m-50m spans)', 'World-class, durable structures ideal for large-scale exhibitions, government programs, and mega weddings. Quick installation and 100% safety compliance with spans ranging from 20m to 50m.', 'Durable German aluminum structures for large-scale events', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Mega Event Structures', 'Hangars'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'german aluminum hangar exhibition structure large scale', true, true, 1),

('Dome Tents & Customized Structures', 'Iconic geodesic domes and custom-engineered tents for luxury, lifestyle, and international-standard events. Perfect for creating unique and memorable event spaces.', 'Custom geodesic domes and luxury event tents', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Mega Event Structures', 'Domes'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'dome tent geodesic custom structure luxury', true, true, 2),

('Waterproof All-Weather Structures', 'Heavy-duty structures designed to withstand wind, rain, and tough outdoor conditions. Ideal for outdoor events requiring reliable weather protection.', 'Weather-resistant structures for outdoor events', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Mega Event Structures', 'Weather Protection'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'waterproof weather resistant outdoor structure', true, true, 3),

-- Climate Control & Power Solutions
('Airwingz Industrial Air Conditioners (15TR & above)', 'Premium event ACs for large venues, with intelligent temperature control, quick 5-hour installation, and energy efficiency. Capacity from 15TR and above.', 'Industrial AC units for large venue climate control', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Climate Control', 'Air Conditioning'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'airwingz industrial AC air conditioner temperature control', true, true, 4),

('Chiller Units (Up to 3000 Tons)', 'Massive cooling capacity for mega exhibitions, defense expos, and hangar setups. Industrial-grade chillers providing reliable temperature control for large spaces.', 'High-capacity chiller units for mega events', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Climate Control', 'Chillers'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'chiller unit cooling capacity mega exhibition', true, true, 5),

('Power Generators (Silent, High-Capacity)', 'Reliable power backup for exhibitions, government shows, and concerts — ensuring uninterrupted performance with silent operation and high capacity output.', 'Silent high-capacity generators for event power', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Power Solutions', 'Generators'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'generator power backup silent high capacity', true, true, 6),

-- Exhibition & Expo Infrastructure
('Maxima Stalls', 'Sleek, modular exhibition stall systems designed for international expos and trade fairs. Professional appearance with flexible configuration options.', 'Premium modular exhibition stall systems', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Exhibition Infrastructure', 'Stalls'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'maxima stall exhibition expo trade fair', true, true, 7),

('Octanorm Stalls (Premium Configurations)', 'Cost-effective yet professional expo booths, customizable with branding. Perfect for trade shows and corporate exhibitions.', 'Professional customizable expo booth systems', 'Mid-Range Pricing', ARRAY['Exhibition Infrastructure', 'Stalls'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'octanorm stall expo booth trade show', true, true, 8),

('Customized Luxury Stalls & Pavilions', 'High-end tailor-made exhibition booths for pharma, auto, defense, and lifestyle expos. Fully customized to brand specifications and requirements.', 'Luxury custom-designed exhibition pavilions', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Exhibition Infrastructure', 'Luxury Stalls'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'luxury custom stall pavilion exhibition booth', true, true, 9),

-- High-End AV & Staging
('LED Video Walls (Indoor & Outdoor)', 'Giant high-resolution LED screens for branding, live streaming, and visual impact. Available in both indoor and outdoor configurations.', 'High-resolution LED display walls for events', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Audio Visual', 'LED Displays'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'LED video wall screen display branding', true, true, 10),

('Professional Concert-Grade Sound Systems', 'High-output systems for mega concerts, rallies, and international events. Professional audio equipment ensuring crystal-clear sound quality.', 'Concert-grade professional sound systems', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Audio Visual', 'Sound Systems'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'concert sound system audio professional', true, true, 11),

('Advanced Lighting Rigs', 'Large-scale stage lighting, spotlights, and intelligent lighting for exhibitions, concerts, and shows. Professional lighting solutions for any event scale.', 'Professional stage and event lighting systems', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Audio Visual', 'Lighting'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'stage lighting rig spotlight intelligent', true, true, 12),

('Special Effects (Lasers, Pyro, Fog Machines)', 'Premium stage effects to elevate entertainment and high-profile events. Professional special effects equipment for memorable experiences.', 'Professional special effects for premium events', 'Premium Pricing', ARRAY['Audio Visual', 'Special Effects'], ARRAY[]::text[], 'special effects laser pyro fog machine', true, true, 13),

